OL,3,CPolice ability to protect public will
OL,4,C'erode' without investment
OL,6,FThe PSNI's financial pressures are so
OL,7,Fsevere that it is "remarkable" that
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland has any officers at
OL,9,Fall, its most senior officer has
OL,10,Fwarned.
OL,12,FPSNI Chief Constable Jon Boutcher said
OL,13,Fthe first job of government is to keep
OL,14,Fpeople safe, but that principle was
OL,15,Fnot being applied in the same way to
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland as other areas.
