OL,3,CPolice ability to protect public will
OL,4,C'erode' without investment
OL,6,FMr Boutcher said: "Let me be clear.
OL,7,FHaving failed to secure the
OL,8,Fprioritisation of the PSNI recovery in
OL,9,Fthe programme for government, without
OL,10,Furgent investment, our ability to
OL,11,Fprotect the public will continue to
OL,12,Ferode.
OL,14,F"Now more than ever we need decisive
OL,15,Faction and investment.
OL,26,@nD@SOUvD@AOU
