OL,3,CPolice ability to protect public will
OL,4,C'erode' without investment
OL,6,F"Had policing kept pace with the
OL,7,Fuplifts in policing in England and
OL,8,FWales, we would have expected the PSNI
OL,9,Fto have been 8,005 and 8,500 police
OL,10,Fofficers. We barely have 6,300.
OL,12,F"A simple Google search asking the
OL,13,Fquestion, what is the first
OL,14,Fresponsibility of government, will
OL,15,Felicit the answer.
OL,17,F"The first judge of government is to
OL,18,Fkeep citizens safe and the country
OL,19,Fsecure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
