OL,3,CPolice ability to protect public will
OL,4,C'erode' without investment
OL,6,F"It is time that principle was applied
OL,7,Fhere as it is everywhere else."
OL,9,FMr Boutcher said he understood the
OL,10,F"wickedly challenging" financial
OL,11,Fissues faced by Stormont ministers,
OL,12,Fbut pointed out they existed elsewhere
OL,13,Fin the UK.
OL,15,FHe said since responsibility for
OL,16,Fpolicing was devolved to Stormont in
OL,17,F2010, the PSNI budget had reduced by
OL,18,F6%.
OL,20,FHe said health and education budgets
OL,21,Fhad risen sharply in the same time.
