OL,6,FMr Boutcher said: "Taking into account
OL,7,Finflationary pressures it is
OL,8,Fremarkable you have any police service
OL,9,Fat all.
OL,11,F"Even a proportionally very small
OL,12,Fuplift over those years to policing,
OL,13,Fnot anywhere near the uplifts provided
OL,14,Fto education or health, would have
OL,15,Fallowed communities in Northern
OL,16,FIreland to be much better served by
OL,17,Fits police service."
